Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'd been traveling through Izu for four days.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.08,0:00:30.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I was filled with wonder and anticipation as I ran.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.71,0:00:34.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Would I catch up with the minstrels,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.20,0:00:37.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,just ahead of me on this Amagi mountain pass?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.68,0:00:41.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Personally, I hoped so.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.14,0:01:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.74,0:01:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.01,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.31,0:01:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.18,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.71,0:01:56.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,This was my third meeting with the dancing girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.30,0:02:00.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,I passed her on the way to Yugashima.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,She had a drum.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,Two days later,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,they came to perform at the inn\N where I was staying,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,and I saw her dancing \Non the wooden floor at the entrance.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.04,0:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, you're soaking wet!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.59,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a fire inside. Why don't you come in and dry off?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this should warm you up.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that troupe pass\N through here very often?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.90,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The minstrels.\N It sounded like you knew them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see them every year.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.70,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think those kinds of geisha \Nmake much money these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.16,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But some people still like them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole family works together.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole family?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The older woman there is the mother,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,followed by her eldest son, \Nhis wife, and younger sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl's name is Kaoru. \NShe seems like a nice girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lucky it cleared up.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk pretty fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a high school student.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.53,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.\N Students often come to our island.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Island? Which one?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oshima.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Port Habu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.34,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of students come for the swimming.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In the summer, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In the winter too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They swim there in the winter?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a silly child!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we part ways, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, he said he'd like to travel with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that sounds wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Journeys are quicker \Nwhen you travel with friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It will certainly make the trip \Nmore interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come join us.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.94,0:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.65,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, take this! \NWhat a little flirt! {https://jisho.org/word/%E8%89%B2%E6%B0%97%E3%81%A5%E3%81%8F}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found a room for you. \NCome, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping there'd be room at your inn.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.97,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly not. It's no place for a gentleman like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you a much nicer place.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice view, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's excellent. Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no trouble. Besides, \Nwe'll be performing here tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll also be coming\N to check out the baths.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all one family, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My wife and I, \Nmy sister, and my mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We enjoy working together.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.62,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.30,0:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose the wrong path in life, \Nso I'll always be poor.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.89,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that at least my younger sister\N won't have to do it for the rest of her life.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you stay a little longer?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.19,0:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we have yet to start\N working tonight. Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your move.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.65,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a strange move. \NYour mind isn't on the game.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mind is on {\i1}other{\i0} games.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.80,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking about that minstrel girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.27,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your move now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.50,0:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru, enough washing. Get into the bath. You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.19,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Get in here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You always act like such a child!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.43,0:09:48.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,I had a full view of the dancing girl's pure white skin.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.80,0:09:54.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,Last night's worries vanished like a dream,\N and I couldn't stop smiling.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.91,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.21,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to try and find more work tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to rest for a while?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.64,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Should we call it\N quits tonight and go visit?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt we'll find any more work.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't be an imposition?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the invitation.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.78,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! How pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a Go board!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Go player?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to play?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.63,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.10,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The innkeeper said we could use their baths. Shall we?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.18,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you join us?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.88,0:11:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wash your back.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.82,0:11:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks, but I just took a bath.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back soon, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play you when I get back.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.85,0:11:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So... can we play now?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Let's play.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be white. You can be black.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you want to play \N"Five in a Row"? {gomokunarabe = gobang (game played on go board involving lining up stones); gomoku; Five in a Row - go is usually played from the outside to the middle, aiming to control more territory, but she placed the first piece on the middle, which is how gomoku is played - from the center to the circumference - not sure how to explain this to the viewer who is unfamiliar with either of those games; in the book translation I have, they just replaced it with checkers}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. I lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One more game!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.08,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go see how they're doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,The next morning,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.04,0:13:10.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,refreshed after the bath, \Nthe troupe headed toward Shimoda.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I went with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,It is indeed more reassuring\N to travel together,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,so Kaoru's mother asked me \Nto accompany them.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Oshima, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.44,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks so huge from here! \NYou'll visit us there, won't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't felt this good in a long time!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some grapes? {yamabudo = crimson glory vine (species of grapevine, Vitis Coignetiae)}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They grow all over the place here! \NGive me a second.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'd only met her two days before,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.59,0:14:32.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,but Kaoru, the dancing girl, \Nhad already stolen my heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.06,0:14:36.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,Some people may say \Nshe's still but a child,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.07,0:14:39.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,but I can't help but feel\N an indescribable admiration
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.55,0:14:44.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,for Kaoru, the young girl \Nwho is trying her best to grow up.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's on your face?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.88,0:15:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wearing such a plain comb?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother bought it for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted a red one, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get a new one for you \Nwhen we get to Shimoda.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.19,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.23,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that's not necessary.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with it. \NI want to buy it for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have to leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.40,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have school, and there are things I need to do first.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept trying to think of a way \Nto postpone it for a day, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.99,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you have nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, \Nour journey was very nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.59,0:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot you'd be leaving once we reached Shimoda.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind \Nif I took Kaoru out tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.67,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might take her to the cinema.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Kaoru. I don't think\N we'll have any work tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we go to the cinema?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here! I'm going to the cinema!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow some money?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.90,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to work.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But brother said...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, but we've been hired to perform.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.95,0:17:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.77,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get ready. \NWe've been suddenly hired.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.17,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let her go this once. \NWhy can't she go to the pictures?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She was looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why she can't go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.64,0:18:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tokyo student could never \Nlove a minstrel girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's just a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She might look that way to you, but she's no longer a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What if that student\N {\i1}does{\i0} come to Oshima,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.60,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kaoru falls in love with him, what are you going to do then?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mizuhara's a nice boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this life, some things just can't be helped,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you're a nice person.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.58,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.68,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.21,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have work. I can't go tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll have to go alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.90,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving on the first boat\N for Tokyo tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.11,0:19:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at dawn, so I may not be able to see you again.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say goodbye\N to your family from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come visit you in Oshima someday.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you worked late last night. \NThanks for coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The picture wasn't all that interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I promised this to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come to Oshima this summer.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:37.75,Song,,0,0,0,,I write a letter to my loved one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:44.36,Song,,0,0,0,,I write and tear it, tear it, and write again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:50.94,Song,,0,0,0,,I throw the rolled up paper at the window {meaning at the glass, probably as a distraction}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:58.63,Song,,0,0,0,,It's raining outside, just like the tears on my cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:05.98,Song,,0,0,0,,Life is a sea, youth is a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:13.07,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, please come and save me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:15.39,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:18.57,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:26.68,Song,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm sinking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:36.65,Song,,0,0,0,,Not a single star in sight, in the sea of ​​sadness
